{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-template-js","path":"/code/java-guide.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2 id=\"java-guide-to-classes\" style=\"position:relative;\">Java Guide to Classes<a href=\"#java-guide-to-classes\" aria-label=\"java guide to classes permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>TCP server socket - <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/net/ServerSocket.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ServerSocket</a></li>\n<li>TCP client socket - <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/net/Socket.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Socket</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"gradle-short-snippets\" style=\"position:relative;\">Gradle short snippets<a href=\"#gradle-short-snippets\" aria-label=\"gradle short snippets permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"add-simple-logger\" style=\"position:relative;\">Add simple logger<a href=\"#add-simple-logger\" aria-label=\"add simple logger permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h3>\n<p><strong>build.gradle</strong></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"groovy\"><pre class=\"language-groovy\"><code class=\"language-groovy\">dependencies <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    implementation <span class=\"token string\">'org.slf4j:slf4j-api:1.7.30'</span>\n    implementation <span class=\"token string\">'org.slf4j:slf4j-simple:1.7.30'</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><strong>Test.java</strong></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token import\"><span class=\"token namespace\">org<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>slf4j<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span></span><span class=\"token class-name\">Logger</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token import\"><span class=\"token namespace\">org<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>slf4j<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span></span><span class=\"token class-name\">LoggerFactory</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Test</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">private</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">final</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Logger</span> logger <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">LoggerFactory</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getLogger</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Test</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Log levels (<a href=\"http://www.slf4j.org/manual.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">manual</a>):</p>\n<ul>\n<li>trace</li>\n<li>error</li>\n<li>warn</li>\n<li>info</li>\n<li>debug</li>\n</ul>\n<p>No \"panic\", no \"warning\"!</p>\n<h3 id=\"slf4j-and-logback\" style=\"position:relative;\">SLF4J and LOGBACK<a href=\"#slf4j-and-logback\" aria-label=\"slf4j and logback permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h3>\n<p>// TODO</p>\n<h2 id=\"plugin-system-in-java\" style=\"position:relative;\">Plugin system in Java<a href=\"#plugin-system-in-java\" aria-label=\"plugin system in java permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>PF4J <a href=\"https://pf4j.org/doc/getting-started.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://pf4j.org/doc/getting-started.html</a></li>\n<li>OSGI</li>\n<li>Custom <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/465099/best-way-to-build-a-plugin-system-with-java\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://stackoverflow.com/questions/465099/best-way-to-build-a-plugin-system-with-java</a> (+ jar loading <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/60764/how-to-load-jar-files-dynamically-at-runtime\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://stackoverflow.com/questions/60764/how-to-load-jar-files-dynamically-at-runtime</a>)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"sandboxing\" style=\"position:relative;\">Sandboxing<a href=\"#sandboxing\" aria-label=\"sandboxing permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3